metadata.name: Shrine of Knight #1/4
metadata.description:
What if the chess piece has their own Shrine  ?  
Knight is the somewhat powerful piece but its move sometimes confuses the newbies, hop over pieces en route to their destination. A surprise attacker, strategic warrior. It acts as the Shrine of War in the land of Chesss-verse  
Shrine of Knight is the second nft editions from the collection.
